Time":"2019-07-23T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"點解無人推呢個post"},{"pid":"5e4b35f2ddc9ebe83e04d93a0fddaefffac49555","tid":1354101,"uid":35194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec8cd08009fec8433b58f45bcd052169acae48e","tid":1354101,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"點解無人推呢個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />魂魄未返黎<br />\n大家返黎啊！！"},{"pid":"40270badff445cd535dbf489e7aac1f957238d46","tid":1354101,"uid":233520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727 建議由元朗站行到大興站散，千萬不要變成「民眾鬥民眾」，這是共產黨最喜愛的，如果雙方有傷亡，到時候是非曲直有理說不清，明益警察及政府可以借此收拾殘局！</span>"}]}